name: ADD
description:
Basic Merge of Deliberate, AnyV3, AnyTWAM and Dreamshaper
+AnyV3 Vae inside

for
making stylized characters. Faces on preview images are built with standart Inpaint of same prompt with increased resolution, no other img2img

modelVersions.description:
Re-trained model and edited some weights now v2 makes better results in realistic faces, more contrast images,

No img2img used for sample images,

Vas is vae-ft-mse-84000
